  _eventId: Echo_ShadowMerchant
  _eventTitle: Shadow Merchant
  _narrative: A cloaked figure materializes from the shadows. 'I deal in trades most
    peculiar,' they whisper. 'What would you give... to gain?'
  _backgroundImage: {fileID: 0}
  _choices:
  - _choiceText: Trade HP for gold (Lose 20 HP)
    _outcomeText: Blood is the currency of the desperate. The merchant seems pleased.
    _outcomes:
    - _type: 4
      _value: 20
      _cardId: 
      _relicId: 
    - _type: 1
      _value: 75
      _cardId: 
      _relicId: 
  - _choiceText: Trade gold for power (Lose 50 gold)
    _outcomeText: The merchant produces a card unlike any you've seen.
    _outcomes:
    - _type: 2
      _value: 50
      _cardId: 
      _relicId: 
    - _type: 14
      _value: 0
      _cardId: 
      _relicId: 
  - _choiceText: Decline
    _outcomeText: The merchant shrugs and fades into shadow. 'Perhaps next time...'
    _outcomes:
    - _type: 0
      _value: 0
      _cardId: 
      _relicId: 
